		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Super Mario in <em>Super Mario Bros.</em> is eight sprites. Mega Man's body is six; his face is an overlay.
<br />
<br />I second others' recommendation of the <a href="http://www.nintendoage.com/faq/NA/nerdy_nights_out.html" class="postlink">Nerdy Nights tutorials on NintendoAge</a>.

		

